《'''minisode 1: Blue Hour'''》是[[韓國|韓國]][[男子音樂團體|男子音樂團體]][[TOMORROW_X_TOGETHER|TOMORROW X TOGETHER]]的第三張韓語迷你專輯，由[[Big_Hit娛樂|Big Hit娛樂]]製作，[[艾利和|IRIVER]]發行，專輯於2020年10月26日發行。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9452637/tomorrow-x-together-minisode1-blue-hour-release-date|title=Tomorrow X Together Announce 'Minisode 1: Blue Hour' EP Release Date|accessdate=2020-09-20|work=|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002210826/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/9452637/tomorrow-x-together-minisode1-blue-hour-release-date|dead-url=no}}</ref>主打歌為〈5시 53분의 하늘에서 발견한 너와 나 (Blue Hour)〉。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/Music/2020/10/20/TXT-dances-in-Blue-Hour-music-video-teaser/5921603215813/|title=TXT dances in 'Blue Hour' music video teaser|accessdate=2020-10-20|work=|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208121636/https://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/Music/2020/10/20/TXT-dances-in-Blue-Hour-music-video-teaser/5921603215813/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==背景及概要==
9月17日，[[韓國|韓國]]媒體採訪報導宣布TOMORROW X TOGETHER將在10月底於[[韓國|韓國]]回歸，而新專輯將會為清涼風格路線，新專輯也是「The Dream Chapter」系列後首張專輯。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/130163|title=TXT 將於 10 月底回歸　新專輯走清涼路線！|accessdate=2020-09-17|work=|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030171641/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/130163|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月21日，所屬經紀公司公開最新預告片，並宣布將於10月26日發行迷你三輯《minisode 1: Blue Hour》。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/art/2020/09/398_296429.html|title=TXT to release mini-album on Oct. 26|accessdate=2020-09-21|work=|language=en}}</ref>

10月23日，所屬經紀公司公開了是次專輯《minisode 1: Blue Hour》的歌單，而當中〈날씨를 잃어버렸어 (We Lost The Summer)〉歌曲由外國歌手[[酷娃恰莉|Charli XCX]]參與創作，是TOMORROW X TOGETHER首次與外國歌手合作的歌曲。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/109/0004295391|title=투모로우바이투게더, 새 앨범 음원 프리뷰 공개..멤버 작사·영국 팝 아티스트 찰리 XCX 참여|accessdate=2020-10-23|work=|language=ko|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101065021/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/109/0004295391|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 商業成績 ==
2020年10月6日，所屬經紀公司宣布迷你三輯《minisode 1: Blue Hour》預購量突破30萬，從9月21日開始預售以來統計了約兩週國內外的訂單量，刷新了TOMORROW X TOGETHER自身的最高紀錄。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/144/0000693670|title=‘빅히트 최강 막내’ 투모로우바이투게더, 새 앨범 선주문 30만 장…역대급 컴백 예고|accessdate=2020-10-06|work=|language=ko|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101000106/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/144/0000693670|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年10月27日， DreamUs Company宣布《minisode 1: Blue Hour》預購量突破40萬，發行的專輯中最高的記錄，專輯亦登上全球30個地區的[[iTunes|iTunes]]排行榜1位，主打歌〈5시 53분의 하늘에서 발견한 너와 나 (Blue Hour)〉的音樂錄影帶在公開20小時後突破700萬觀看次數。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/131158|title=TXT 回歸前開紅盤　新專輯創出道以來最佳預購量！|accessdate=2020-10-26|work=|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108081245/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/131158|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年10月27日，主打曲〈5시 53분의 하늘에서 발견한 너와 나 (Blue Hour)〉進入MelOn 24Hits，使TOMORROW X TOGETHER成為第四位男團進入MelOn 24Hits的榜單。根據Hanteo排行榜數據，《minisode 1: Blue Hour》發行僅兩日銷售量突破19萬張，刷新了迷你二輯《[[The_Dream_Chapter:_ETERNITY|The Dream Chapter: ETERNITY]]》首週銷售紀錄。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.soompi.com/article/1434126wpp/txt-tops-itunes-charts-around-the-globe-with-minisode1-blue-hour|title=TXT Tops iTunes Charts Around The Globe With “minisode1 : Blue Hour”|accessdate=2020-10-27|work=|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101120322/https://www.soompi.com/article/1434126wpp/txt-tops-itunes-charts-around-the-globe-with-minisode1-blue-hour|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/131212|title=TXT 詮釋青春變化引發的微妙情緒　〈minisode1 : Blue Hour〉橫掃 30 國 iTunes 專輯榜！|accessdate=2020-10-27|work=|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103035656/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/131212|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年11月17日，根據《[[告示牌|告示牌]]》報導，TOMORROW X TOGETHER迷你三輯《minisode 1: Blue Hour》於「[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|Billboard 200]]」名列第25名，成為自身和新生代韓團中「[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|Billboard 200]]」最高排名的專輯。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/311/0001228118|title=투모로우바이투게더, 美 ‘빌보드 200’ 26위…K팝 유망주 입증|date=2020-11-17|accessdate=2020-11-17|work=|language=ko|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122231851/https://n.news.naver.com/entertain/article/311/0001228118|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年5月26日，主打歌〈5시 53분의 하늘에서 발견한 너와 나 (Blue Hour)〉的音樂錄影帶歷時211天突破一億觀看次數，成為TOMORROW X TOGETHER最快突破一億觀看次數的音樂錄影帶，亦是TOMORROW X TOGETHER第二首破億的音樂錄影帶。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.soompi.com/article/1471253wpp/txts-blue-hour-becomes-their-2nd-mv-to-surpass-100-million-views|title=TXT’s “Blue Hour” Becomes Their 2nd MV To Surpass 100 Million Views|work=|date=2021-05-26|accessdate=2021-05-27|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210601041605/https://www.soompi.com/article/1471253wpp/txts-blue-hour-becomes-their-2nd-mv-to-surpass-100-million-views|dead-url=no}}</ref>

